{"word":"G5185 - τυφλός - typhlós - toof-los' - Blind","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">τυφλός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">typhlós</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">toof-los'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Blind</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"குருடான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"blind"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5187 - τυφόω - typhóō - toof-o'-o/5187\">G5187</a>; <i>opaque</i> (as if <i>smoky</i>), that is, (by analogy) <i>blind</i> (physically or mentally): - blind.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G5185/5185\">G5185</a>, <a href=\"#/G5186/5186\">G5186</a>"}]}